Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\bord0\shad0\fad(417,458)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\pos(640,538)}联合国军最终决战舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs43\bord0\shad0\fad(417,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\pos(640,510)}「雾」之大舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军目标健在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的攻击都失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,人类剩下的所有战力都集中到这场战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此的数量依然无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,21世纪初
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,人类由于全球变暖等影响 失去了地上的绝大多数版图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就像在呼应这一情况一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真相不明的「雾」之大战舰群出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,封锁了所有运输航道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,人类从所有的海洋中被驱赶了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HEFE9E1&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(332,588)}分散式首都 东京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在最终决战后的7年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,政治与经济纷纷崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,通信卫星和海底电缆也被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,并且由于它们释放的电磁干扰 所有的通信都被封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,各国均无奈地处于孤立状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就连互相是否存在也无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(404,588)}佐贺县航天发射中心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把状况显示到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的「雾」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗅探到里面的东西了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,给我挡住它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持到发射的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快点准备发射SSTO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.05,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an7\bord1}SSTO（Single-Stage to Orbit）：可在宇宙空间飞行，能多次使用的超音速运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,540)}「雾」之舰队 东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,702)}轻巡洋舰长良
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(544,588)}航天发射中心导弹防御系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,天津风号与太刀风号沉没！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,「雾」马上将脱离水雷区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就没有什么对策了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所属不明的潜艇正迅速接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人的增援么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这个信号特征…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是 伊号401！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HE7E7E7&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,597)}「雾」之潜艇 I-401
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们接受的委托内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止「雾」的前进 亦或是将其击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,直到SSTO发射成功为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,伊欧娜 报告数据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,长良级轻巡洋舰 长良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,排水量6010吨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,装备有强制波动装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,12.3cm口径连装炮塔3座6门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舰底部装备有鱼雷发射管12门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,此外还拥有激光高射炮3门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有导弹发射模块 近防武器系统等多数武装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最大速度60节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有潜水能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,标准的「雾」之轻巡洋舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,杏平！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,各鱼雷装填
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,七号发射管 侵蚀鱼雷发射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,检测到高速推进音 两枚鱼雷正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被发现了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,1-2号发射管 速射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭引擎 下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,急速下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,展开克莱因力场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\an7\bord1}克莱因力场（Klein Field）：强制波动装甲产生的力场，能生成形似克莱因瓶的通道偏转能量\N所以称为克莱因力场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,距鱼雷击中还有 5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,侵蚀型鱼雷即将命中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\an8}2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\an8}1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,长良 转向右舷 同时展开克莱因力场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太迟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,伊号401… 苍蓝钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord1\blur2\shad0\c&HFFFCFF&\3c&H3D3836&\pos(647,499)}航路所有者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大陆间联络用SSTO发射成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,呼 哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在日本难道还有东西可以送去外国吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是有才发射的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,长良 你只是服从命令罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伊欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为使用克莱因力场有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,「雾」是为什么出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,又是为了什么而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是单纯的为了服从命令而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为我的命令才战斗着么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是您的舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从两年前醒来的那时起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(960,589)}2年前 横须贺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(915,594)}海洋技术综合学院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,千早群像这次也被选入了视察小组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为成绩很优秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.24,text,,0,0,0,,{\fr5\fs30\pos(573.6,20.8)}公告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.24,text,,0,0,0,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(583.467,151.466)}下列人员请在指定的时间前往指定的地点报道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.24,text,,0,0,0,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(476.496,222.78)}日期: 9月14日  14:00～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.24,text,,0,0,0,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(502.782,268.494)}地点: 干部候补生校舍201讲堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.24,text,,0,0,0,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(479.011,308.265)}人员名单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.24,text,,0,0,0,,{\fr5\fs20\pos(698.744,629.598)}海洋技术学院 校长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不止这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,千早是牺牲的舰长大人的独生子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们不同 他是被优待的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,说到那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他的父亲投奔「雾」的谣传是真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大海战的情报又没公开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 千早总有些黑幕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来你们看到的东西将是最重要军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只被许可对你们这些将来受期待的学生公开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要机密…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,早晚会成为士官的你们有知道的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这只不过是组织上传达事项罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\shad0\bord1\c&HDEDEDE&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(980,595)}第51号仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,潜水艇 伊号401…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是被捕获的「雾」的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,外观虽是模仿太平洋战争的潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,却不是人造之物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,上面居然还藏着这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 这不是能公开的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在大海战后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这艘潜水艇锁定了武装出现在了这个港口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其理由目的均未知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙毫无抵抗被我们捕获了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能解明这艘船的原理的话 说不定「雾」的弱点也能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们已经研究了7年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已经把能想到的手段全部尝试了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙还是不让我们进入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说解体也做不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是十分丢脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,「雾」的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的…敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,千早… 群像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快收集数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是 引力反应？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,401 启动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别让它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,关上天花板的防护壁 现在赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退！ 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们学校有那样一个人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 千早群像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字吖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是在找谁么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,超级 美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我没有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 是个美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是 千早群像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,千早翔像的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,「去见千早翔像的儿子」我被这样命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,新的恶作剧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就光想些无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 这不是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么为什么会提到我去世的父亲的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伊欧娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我被起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伊欧娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在这不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上 你一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,群像 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样死脑筋的人反而被搭讪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,软呼呼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是人类的…感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,能说明把我叫出来的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的说 是我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没时间陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,距离起床时间还有11个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想为没意义的事情浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我 没意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你就直接说有什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,「去见千早翔像的儿子群像 并听从他的命令」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我记忆里 唯一的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我在七年间一直与外部隔离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,七年？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是服从于命令…的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,千早群像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我被吩咐要服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,确认：你的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想拥有能打破当下这种停滞状态的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就算留在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能平静地度过毫无意义的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我活着不是为了做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,终于 我可以启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-401 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-401 从机密码头离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,401…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…「雾」么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一知道的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你接触 然后服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我记忆里 唯一的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,服从命令而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们渴望着命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,401
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你成为我的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,群像…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,乘上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿过屏障了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要反击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能承受得住么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让人进入我这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,演算来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,潜航呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,引力子稳定器初始设定还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,距离力场还有5秒消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,4…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,3…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,2…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱因力场消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舰尾中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我现在什么都无法改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就和死没什么区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,引力子稳定器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,设定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,进入待机状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,潜下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,401 丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是 没有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,被动声纳有反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.87,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\an7}被动声呐：也叫噪声声呐，不发出任何讯号，只接收和处理水中目标发出的辐射噪声或声呐信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在索敌范围内没有敌舰反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的第一位舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,401…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伊欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的记忆中我是被取了这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,伊欧娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,从那时候开始 我们一直是逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我是舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,带我一起去 为了找到群像所寻求的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛了「雾」的人 蛮不错的答卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\shad0\bord1\c&HEFE9E1&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(952,595)\fad(0,400)}分散式首都 长崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,596)}军务省助理秘书长 上阴龙二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这次SSTO的事辛苦你了 千早群像君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是委托人上阴先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能早点雇佣我的话 军队的损失就能减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,由于「雾」的干扰 我们无法长距离通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说这种强人所难的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 大人有大人的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,政治么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是诡辩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们只是在绕道而行不是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是每个人都能像你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也有从事着肮脏工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 既然委托完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他出了什么事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会被「她」攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,千早君 你这样战斗下去会有出路么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说 我对你在这两年间与「雾」战斗的战绩有很高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚收到消息说 SSTO被摧毁在卫星轨道上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个上面搭载有日本研究开发的最新兵器「振动弹头」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,「振动弹头」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在你跟「雾」孤军战斗的两年间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也并没有闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是美国？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,日本已经没有能够量产它们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,千早群像君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个工作想委托给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望你能运送它…这个人类的希望 最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵器是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是解析了「雾」的侵蚀鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,并且改良了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,作为黑箱未知的部分虽然还很多是没错 但是如果能量产的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,人类说不定就能迎来反击的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要是美国还存在的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说这么不吉利的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这件事跟美国的秘密协定大概是三个月前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,之后就停止了联络
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是什么状况也完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伊欧娜 真的不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我被切断了与其他船只的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能知道的就只有自己发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只有海上直接运输这一条路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大陆现在十分的内乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,通过内陆去运送反而很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就连同胞人类也无法信任什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 舰长接受了这份委托是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也只有我们能完成这份委托
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,新武器样本的接收将在横须贺港
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,航路设定为横须贺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们去接收人类的希望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的希望…么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆压制了I-401 不是更好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,401 是有自我意识的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它只服从千早群像的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,心智模型么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.17,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}心智模型（Mental Model）：「雾」之舰队伊型潜艇以及重巡洋舰以上级别才拥有的人型意志体，\N每艘都有独立意志，并可互相沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,「雾」的叛徒和人类的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,十分有趣的组合不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HB5C5DB&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(249.6,588)}佐渡洋面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\bord1\shad0\c&HD5D2CF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,540)\fad(0,400)}「雾」之舰队 东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HD5D2CF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,699)\fad(0,400)}旗舰·战列舰金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,长良被击沉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个身体也差不多习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是让人厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明明是兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:21:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,摩耶么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\bord1\shad0\c&HDAE8FA&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(805.667,535.333)}久米岛洋面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\shad0\c&HDAE8FA&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(1097,604)}「雾」之舰队 \N东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HDAE8FA&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(916,651)}重巡洋舰摩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,401不都出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,难道就没有什么可以做的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,北面的话 是高雄的管辖范围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,交给那孩子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能别管什么管辖范围么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,服从海军最高密令的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs-3\pos(616.4,657)}Admiralty Code
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.98,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs34}海军最高密令（Admiralty Code）：「雾」之舰队正在寻找的神秘密令，又称「失落的敕命」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,金刚你这石头脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,高雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\bord1\shad0\c&HC9C7D3&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(808,531)}远州洋面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\shad0\c&HC9C7D3&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(1097,604)}「雾」之舰队\N 东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HC9C7D3&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(941.6,653.2)}重巡洋舰高雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,401往这边来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,加入了人类的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我高雄将她化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}I look across a raging war and feel the steady beating of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:53.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}嵐の前の靜けさに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:56.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}刃を振り下ろしていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}繰り返しa memory fading 今も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:18.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}時代を超えてI tell a story響く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:23.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}宣戦布告の詩 残酷に染もる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:25.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}この誓いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:29.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}We'll fight until the bitter end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}途切れた息の根を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:36.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}汚れた世界を繋ぎ止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}僕らの歯車を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}it's time to Stop & Rewind(Stop & Rewind)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:43.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}失った冀望を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:46.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}壞れた時間のピースを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:48.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}取り戻す為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:51.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}you need to Fall & Unwind(Fall & Unwind)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}走り出す鼓動さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}限りない慈しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}導き出すアルペジオ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}Savior of Song
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}A Savior of Song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我望向激烈的战场 感受我心脏不断的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:53.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}迎着暴风雨前的寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:56.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}手起刀落斩开平淡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}反反复复的记忆也已褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:18.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}慢慢讲述超越时空的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:23.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}宣战之歌已染上残酷的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:25.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}这份誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:29.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我们要血战到底直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}将骤然停止的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:36.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}与这污秽的世界相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我们身上滚动的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}是时候令其倒回重来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:43.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}找回失去的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:46.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}收集破碎的时间断片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:48.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}为了去取回失去之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:51.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}你只需跟从脚步放下包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}充斥迈向前方的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}与无边无际的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}演奏出美丽的琶音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}救歌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}这是救歌之人
